{
  "stem": "1282.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But on Sunday mornings, my father put it out in the window, and as the Gentile kids came out of church. or the Gentile people, 100, 200, 300 at a time, sat around the house and my father put on the radio in the window, turned on Budapest station and listen to it.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were always get excited because things were always happening around our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My father and the priest were intimate friends because they had mutual respect.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father was a religious, the priest was religious, but my father was modern enough to respect and gain respect.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was this, this-- that was the kind of life-- very simple, very humble, small community.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But yes, that was happiness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Wooden toys and-- but they were happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were happy moments.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I do not have sad memories of my childhood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have-- my greatest regret that I was never able to tell my father how wonderful they were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've suffered, but that's [INAUDIBLE] because they were good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were good parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were loving parents, and I--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not have a chance to say thank you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I am, basically, for what I have learned as a child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I did is, after I lost my wife, I went through a sort of depression.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fortunately it was not a deep enough depression where I couldn't function.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was functional depression for a year or two.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everything-- so I did seek out help on a few occasions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of the things that was very disturbing to me, because of the loss of my wife, I also suffered again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did not suffer the loss of my parents when I was very young because I didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was a kid, and you handle it differently.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
